{"tid":1427574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[前線入]令魔法力大幅增強","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:29:34.000Z","uid":283781,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f65114ae1bf2cb04745904e57b08522a697c3847","tid":1427574,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"最近開始見到有豪火球之術倍感安慰<br />\n不過見魔法力都暫時唔係好大<br />\n所以我覺得前線既手足<br />\n應該一人一個玻璃樽/水彈 放滿魔法液<br />\n等魔法師發號施令<br />\n大家一齊放魔法液 等法師再放<br />\n到時魔法力大增<br />\n始終魔法進可攻退可守<br />\n依家既魔法力仲未可以令我地築成防線<br />\n<br />\n講到呢到相信好多人都擔心tk之類<br />\n我就反而最擔心記者<br />\n有冇方法可以令魔法大增又唔tk<br />\n同埋其實有幾多前線敢掟<br />\n問左幾個frd都前線救火兵都唔敢"},{"pid":"ba0e1f8bb6b514f57d0eee18a0ce3aa09b1cb413","tid":1427574,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"96284cceb0c2107ffe05c98ca654a304f8ee893b","tid":1427574,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed6d753449dc740e1386caf5882584ff01df2d2","tid":1427574,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"Push 我要增強法術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0795f26558e21a6e54dfc6c630e2e01aee1922","tid":1427574,"uid":229641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22557679b039b67592498dbd9ad786531afd6f0f","tid":1427574,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c